{"type": "article", "id": 50285, "title": "Gucci 年收入超 60 亿欧，以及，老爸鞋推出了全新配色 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-02-14T03:16:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 47266, "name": "狗年"}, {"id": 6467, "name": "红包"}, {"id": 189, "name": "Burberry"}, {"id": 1128, "name": "LGBT"}, {"id": 905, "name": "Dover Street Market"}, {"id": 3203, "name": "Balenciaga"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 5170, "name": "Moncler"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180214110209p1wh9GKcn60V5MBT.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/kering-sees-continued-mileage-gucci-1202560407/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>开云集团去年营收大涨，Gucci 超 60 亿欧元</strong></a> | 开云发布第四季度财报，截止 12 月 31 日的三个月内销售额增长 42.6% 至 18.2 亿欧元。 2017 年全年，集团净营收达到 17.8 亿欧元，同比增长 119.5%；运营利润达到 29.5 欧元，同比增长 56.3%，为历史最高水平。旗下品牌中，Gucci 表现最好，年销售额大涨 41.9% 至 62.11 亿欧元，也是首次超过 60 亿欧元。Bottega Veneta 增长 0.2%，为 11.76 亿欧元。Yves Saint Laurent 增长 23%，至 15.01 亿欧元。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/business-features/monclers-new-strategy-appears-to-be-eight-is-enough-1202559408/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Moncler 推出新的设计策略</strong></a> | 过去十年，Moncler 与 Thom Browne 和 Giambattista Valli 分别合作推出 Moncler Gamme Bleu 与 Gamme Rouge 这两个男女装系列，未来则将换成 8 位设计师，每人各负责一个系列。这些新系列将于 2 月 20 日米兰时装周秀场上亮相。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>马上就要过年啦。<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/dover-street-market-year-of-the-dog-capsule/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dover Street Market</a> 联合 NikeLab、Noah、Stussy、Undercover、A Bathing Ape 等多个品牌，推出了 2018 新春生肖特辑。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105737QrGmLI1qKWb4UXko.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105736nUY6NFyBA0dbRrTw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802141057335YjO9JG238dBbWTc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105731hOfFRgBs6vraKpLY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018021410573545xgVvI8NX9oLmht.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802141057355ljQpdh4tzOyv2Af.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105738x6mDB9OXSt5wzVk2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebae.com/2018/2/balenciaga-triple-s-sneakers-new-colorways-ladies-where-to-buy\" rel=\"nofollow\">Balenciaga </a>大热的老爸鞋 Triple S，一口气推出了六款全新配色，其中荧光黄和粉色的那双只有女性的尺码。 </p><p>STYLEBOP.COM 现在已经开售这个新系列了，每双售价大约为 827 美元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105645gNrViyQ2fp1s8Pqu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105646p2brleiaQcm1UM9n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105647OYyxFosfjmdnJNS4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105647mutvx36MH2iqXPgK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105649ZEbmNvk3w5hgB0M1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105648POd0bXLm9rZV7UsI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105648zBjKs3fOFD5puU7y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105648HPm2oLUfbkA8qEi6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802141056493DiEtbZpSHIWe1v2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802141056495f9iF4JCbtQc8KOV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105644yJMeYG3XBcz04arV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105656u0ia1FxlnXgU6ZYy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>2 月 18 日即将发售的 2018 系列里，<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/02/13/burberry-creates-rainbow-tartan-support-lgbt-charities/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Burberry </a>更新了经典的格子呢，使用了彩虹色表示对 LGBT 运动的支持。Burberry 称其为“乐观和包容的象征”。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105607s7zlAIKhOXUunrB5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018021410560718s0397u5varXlnV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105616XMQfgiLONA8Y4wFc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.242424\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>纽约潮牌 <a href=\"https://search.fashionsnap.com/collection/rag_bone/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rag&amp;Bone </a>的 2018 秋冬系列衣服不错，lookbook 里模特的肢体语言相当丰富... </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105536LmihIDMEadsPUk0q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105537Bip49xO8CzAvhb2u.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105537bcpOWUTjNfgI1v7G.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105537S4I1CbKTP7l9RQao.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105537eXEdi0SP5YUvFz9D.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105538DwOsLRn3mr05ytdS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105539jB6CiETZfvWsk7br.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105540TQEZk3Jb9zfFde1u.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802141055401yegBArxD4sk7GFN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105541IkLsNZ2wb4ufWCnP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105541bWgd9ni1D5upTs3J.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802141055410f7YZ6nviAzljVMD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105542PB1v5fCl7Ru48IUb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180214105542lUks8nmRGToWZh6z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>看完了一言难尽的狗年生肖限定款衣服、包包、彩妆，来看看<a href=\"http://www.harpersbazaar.com.tw/fashion/news/news/g2019/2018-red-envelope/\" rel=\"nofollow\">各大奢侈品牌特制的狗年红包</a>。<br></p><p>相比各种狗年限定款，这些红包要好看多了。比如爱马仕的狗狗、Fendi 浮夸的礼盒，还有 Prada 做成 Cashier 样子的红包，都还挺有趣的。